        {
            "body": "<p>Skill descriptions adhere to the following guidelines.</p>", 
            "source": "Core Rulebook", 
            "type": "section"
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>The skill name line includes (in addition to the name of the skill) the following information.</p>", 
            "name": "Skill Name", 
            "url": "pfsrd://Core Rulebook/Rules/Using Skills/Skill Descriptions/Skill Name", 
            "type": "section", 
            "source": "Core Rulebook", 
            "sections": [
                {
                    "body": "<p class=\"stat-block-2\">The abbreviation of the ability whose modifier applies to the skill check.</p>", 
                    "url": "pfsrd://Core Rulebook/Rules/Using Skills/Skill Descriptions/Skill Name/Key Ability", 
                    "type": "section", 
                    "name": "Key Ability", 
                    "source": "Core Rulebook"
                }, 
                {
                    "body": "<p class=\"stat-block-2\">If this notation is included in the skill name line, you must have at least 1 rank in the skill to use it. If this notation is omitted, the skill can be used untrained (with a rank of 0). If any special notes apply to trained or untrained use, they are covered in the Untrained section (see below).</p>", 
                    "url": "pfsrd://Core Rulebook/Rules/Using Skills/Skill Descriptions/Skill Name/Trained Only", 
                    "type": "section", 
                    "name": "Trained Only", 
                    "source": "Core Rulebook"
                }, 
                {
                    "body": "<p class=\"stat-block-2\">If this notation is included in the skill name line, an armor check penalty applies (see Equipment) to checks using this skill. If this entry is absent, an armor check penalty does not apply.</p>", 
                    "url": "pfsrd://Core Rulebook/Rules/Using Skills/Skill Descriptions/Skill Name/Armor Check Penalty", 
                    "type": "section", 
                    "name": "Armor Check Penalty", 
                    "source": "Core Rulebook"
                }
            ]
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>The skill name line is followed by a general description of what using the skill represents.</p>", 
            "source": "Core Rulebook", 
            "type": "section", 
            "name": "Description"
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>What a character (&ldquo;you&rdquo; in the skill description) can do with a successful skill check and the check's Difficulty Class (DC).</p>", 
            "source": "Core Rulebook", 
            "type": "section", 
            "name": "Check"
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>The type of action using the skill requires, or the amount of time required for a check.</p>", 
            "source": "Core Rulebook", 
            "type": "section", 
            "name": "Action"
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>Any conditions that apply to successive attempts to use the skill successfully. If the skill doesn't allow you to attempt the same task more than once, or if failure carries an inherent penalty (such as with the Climb skill), you can't take 20. If this paragraph is omitted, the skill can be retried without any inherent penalty other than the additional time required.</p>", 
            "source": "Core Rulebook", 
            "type": "section", 
            "name": "Try Again"
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>Any extra facts that apply to the skill, such as special effects deriving from its use or bonuses that certain characters receive because of class, feat choices, or race.</p>", 
            "source": "Core Rulebook", 
            "type": "section", 
            "name": "Special"
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>The full utility of certain skills is restricted to characters of certain classes. This entry indicates whether any such restrictions exist for the skill.</p>", 
            "url": "pfsrd://Core Rulebook/Rules/Using Skills/Skill Descriptions/Restriction", 
            "type": "section", 
            "name": "Restriction", 
            "source": "Core Rulebook"
        }, 
        {
            "body": "<p>This entry indicates what a character without at least 1 rank in the skill can do with it. If this entry doesn't appear, it means that the skill functions normally for untrained characters (if it can be used untrained) or that an untrained character can't attempt checks with this skill (for skills that are designated &ldquo;Trained Only&rdquo;).</p>", 
            "url": "pfsrd://Core Rulebook/Rules/Using Skills/Skill Descriptions/Untrained", 
            "type": "section", 
            "name": "Untrained", 
            "source": "Core Rulebook"
        }
    ]
}